room_title: Escape room "Wonderland" by ​Escape Bloomington in Bloomington
room_description: You're late, you're late for a very important date! The Queen is demanding an audience with you in sixty minutes and not one minute later. The last person who was late for a meeting with her majesty was....well lets just say heads rolled that day. On your way to the Queen’s castle you stumble across a strange man in a large hat having what appears to be a Party in the middle of the woods. You explain you are on your way to meet the queen and cannot be late, but the man will not take no for an answer. You suddenly find yourself suddenly sitting at his strange table with the trees closing in around you. There seems to be no way out. Will you escape the party and meet the Queen on time or will you end up on the chopping block?
